{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "api/**/*.js",
      "use": "@vercel/node"
    },
    {
      "src": "*.html",
      "use": "@vercel/static"
    }
  ],
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/api/kite-data",
      "dest": "/api/kite-data.js"
    },
    {
      "src": "/(.*)",
      "dest": "/$1"
    }
  ]
}
```

### **Make Sure Your File Structure is Correct:**
```
ridawn-stock-exchange/
├── api/
│   └── kite-data.js       ← Must be here
├── index.html             ← Must be in root
├── admin.html             ← Must be in root
├── vercel.json            ← Must be in root
└── package.json           ← Must be in root
